Usage: specifyClockToDataSpacing [-help] {{-cell <string> {[-x <float> ] [-y <float> ]}} | -reset }

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # specify clock cell (string, optional)
-reset             # clear all clock-to-data spacing rules (bool, optional)
-x <float>         # specify spacing on both left/right sides (float, optional)
-y <float>         # specify spacing on both top/bottom sides (float, optional)